                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Chris hayman"
            },
            "reviewBody": "Have cooked this recipe most weeks for the last two years and everyone raves about it - just come back from 4 weeks in Hungary Rumania Albania Montenegro Macedonia Serbia etc and pls to report none of the goulash I tried was as good as this recipe 👍👍"
        },
        {
            "@type": "Review",
            "author": {
                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Bogi"
            },
            "reviewBody": "It's not made this way in Hungary, although it's definitely delicious, but it's not \"gulyas\"."
        },
        {
            "@type": "Review",
            "author": {
                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Peggy Fergus"
            },
            "reviewBody": "We tried this last week and it was wonderful. It is now our official Hungarian goulash recipe and will be on a regular rotation. And yes, use ALL that paprika!"
        },
